{"tid":1380721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<睇急症>想補充番，醫院絕對<可以>拍攝的","createTime":"2019-07-29T05:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T06:54:39.000Z","uid":137220,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"07760f8e38d9741934ed715b100299fd596f1f03","tid":1380721,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"[url]我係急症室醫生，教你發夢受傷點樣睇醫生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1376835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1376835</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n<br />\n上面個post講，醫院附例禁止拍攝，其實係錯的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap113A!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap113A%21zh-Hant-HK&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67UYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=e9134d75\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap113A!zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n醫院附例 係點講？<br />\n<br />\n113A, 7，禁止作出某些行為<br />\n(1)任何人不得在醫院內 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n..... <br />\n(f)<span style=\"color: red;\">未經醫院內病人同意</span>，拍攝照片、影片或錄像影片，把其容貌勾劃出來；或  (1991年第436號法律公告)<br />\n(g)未經院方職員同意，拍攝照片、影片或錄像影片，把醫院病房勾劃出來，<span style=\"color: red;\">而除非拍攝工作對病人造成或有可能造成煩擾或打擾，或對病人的治療造成或有可能造成不良影響，否則院方職員不得拒絕讓該等拍攝工作進行。</span>  (1991年第436號法律公告)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上所講，只要病人，即係你同意，你係可以拍攝自己，甚至拍攝犬黎保障自己<br />\n<br />\n好多人都唔知架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d8006fba1d4a2f5352e017e06ebf58373b240e","tid":1380721,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3abb4a550188f26dd07c351394a43aba76d8b0f","tid":1380721,"uid":279266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07760f8e38d9741934ed715b100